g; Phase 17 Wave 0 must define at least one CLI/API entry."}, {"at": "2026-06-03T20:45:00Z", "action": "resolve", "note": "Three user-visible entry points created and E2E verified: 1. CLI: kos capture <url|text> + kos search <query> 2. Web UI: GET /capture (form) + POST /api/capture + GET / (search) 3. Hermes skill: capture/搜 commands with LLM enrichment E2E flow verified: web_extract → LLM summarization + entity extraction → kos capture → kos ingest → kos search → formatted results. Agora web dashboard running on port 7430."}], "closure_evidence_refs": ["projects/kairon/packages/kos/src/kos/cli/__main__.py", "projects/kairon/packages/kos/src/kos/web/app.py", ".hermes/skills/knowledge-capture-search/SKILL.md", "LAYER-INDEX.md"], "closure_summary": "Knowledge Capture/Search Pilot E2E completed. Three entry points established (CLI, Web UI, Hermes skill). Full pipeline verified: content capture → LLM enrichment → KOS indexing → FTS5 search → formatted results. Agora service mesh operational on 7430/7431. All 6 original debt items closed.\n", "x3_tier": "Theory", "x1_policy_refs": ["X1-AUDIT-001", "X1-AUTH-001"], "x2_rules": ["X2-LIFECYCLE-001", "X2-LIFECYCLE-002"], "x2_freshness": ""}, {"id": "R2_AGORA_NOT_RUNNING", "title": "Agora Service Mesh 未运行 — 端口 7430/7431 无监听", "dimension": "architecture", "subdimension": "service_mesh", "domain": "projects", "scope": "cross_project", "severity": "low", "weight": 0.15, "entropy_class": "state", "lifecycle_state": "closed", "owner": "agora-maintainer", "affected_roots": ["projects/kairon/packages/agora"], "evidence_refs": [".omo/_knowledge/management/architecture-health-snapshot-phase16-post.md"], "mitigation_refs": [".omo/_knowledge/design/phase17-planning-gate-guardrails.md"], "opened_at": "2026-06-03T14:50:00Z", "resolved_at": "2026-06-03T20:45:00Z", "last_reviewed_at": "2026-06-03T20:45:00Z", "next_review_at": "2026-07-03T00:00:00Z", "gate_level": "phase17", "history": [{"at": "2026-06-03T14:50:00Z", "action": "register", "note": "Agora code is healthy (49 tests, app.py/cli.py present) but ports 7430/7431 have no listener. LAYER-INDEX incorrectly marks as running. Phase 17 Wave 0 must include Agora startup as hard prerequisite."}, {"at": "2026-06-03T20:45:00Z", "action": "resolve", "note": "Agora web dashboard started on port 7430 (verified: health endpoint returns OK). Agora MCP SSE server started on port 7431 (verified: connected to 19 downstream MCP services). Dependency fix: added shared-lib to agora workspace dependencies. LAYER-INDEX updated to 🟢 running."}], "closure_evidence_refs": ["LAYER-INDEX.md"], "closure_summary": "Agora service mesh operational. Web dashboard running on 7430, MCP SSE proxy on 7431. Health check endpoints verified. Dependency gap (shared-lib) resolved.\n", "x3_tier": "Framework", "x1_policy_refs": ["X1-AUDIT-002"], "x2_rules": ["X2-LIFECYCLE-001", "X2-LIFECYCLE-002"], "x2_freshness": ""}, {"id": "R3_LAYER_INDEX_DRIFT", "title": "LAYER-INDEX 与实际状态不一致 — 多处过时标记", "dimension": "documentation", "subdimension": "accuracy", "domain": "workspace", "scope": "cross_project", "severity": "low", "weight": 0.1, "entropy_class": "pointer", "lifecycle_state": "closed", "owner": "docs-governance", "affected_roots": ["LAYER-INDEX.md"], "evidence_refs": [".omo/_knowledge/management/architecture-health-snapshot-phase16-post.md"], "mitigation_refs": [".omo/_knowledge/design/phase17-planning-gate-guardrails.md"], "opened_at": "2026-06-03T14:50:00Z", "resolved_at": "2026-06-03T20:30:00Z", "last_reviewed_at": "2026-06-03T20:30:00Z", "next_review_at": "2026-07-03T00:00:00Z", "gate_level": "phase17", "history": [{"at": "2026-06-03T14:50:00Z", "action": "register", "note": "LAYER-INDEX marks Agora as running (it's not), SharedBrain as having 19 organs (organs/ deleted), D-Memory/D-Harvest as active (organs archived). DECOMPOSITION.md path pointer wrong (SharedBrain/_archived/ vs projects/_archived/). Phase 17 Wave 0 must update LAYER-INDEX before Wave 1."}, {"at": "2026-06-03T20:3